title: Ep 47: Cults
description:
This week I have a special guest. Jessica was brought into a cult by her parents at the age of 8. After suffering years of abuse, she got out and is now a happy, thriving woman. How do you get sucked into a cult, how do you get out and how do you go on after being one? All these questions and more! 

"Life is fucked, but we're here for some reason." - Jessica
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
